// Vitest Snapshot v1, https://vitest.dev/guide/snapshot.html

exports[`renderCopilot > matches snapshot 1`] = `
"# Copilot instructions for this repository

- **Stack:** TypeScript, Next.js 14 App Router (web-app).
- **Packages to respect:** next, react, tailwindcss, @radix-ui/react-slot, class-variance-authority, clsx, ….
- **Package manager:** pnpm.
- **Files:** Kebab-case for \`app/\` route segments; PascalCase for components under \`components/\`. Colocate feature modules under \`features/<name>/\`.
- **Components:** PascalCase file names matching the default export. Prefer composing primitives from \`components/ui/\` (shadcn) rather than one-off styled divs.
- **Functions / variables:** camelCase for utilities and hooks (\`useTheme\`). Event handlers prefixed with \`handle\` or passed as \`onX\` props.; camelCase locals; SCREAMING_SNAKE only for true constants. Prefer \`const\` and narrow types with \`satisfies\` where helpful.
- **Layout:** Routes and layouts live in \`app/\` (App Router). Shared UI primitives live in \`components/ui/\` (shadcn). Shared helpers in \`lib/\` (e.g. \`lib/utils.ts\` with \`cn()\`). Global styles in \`app/globals.css\`; Tailwind v4 via \`@tailwindcss/postcss\`.
- **Errors:** Use \`try/catch\` in Server Actions and surface user-facing errors with Sonner toasts on the client. Prefer returning typed Result-like objects from server utilities when batching work.
- **State:** React state and context for local UI; server state from \`fetch\` in Server Components. No global client store unless a route truly needs it.
- **Tests (Vitest):** Vitest + Testing Library for components; colocate \`*.test.tsx\` next to components or under \`__tests__/\`. Run \`pnpm test\` from repo root.
- **Pattern \`lib/utils.ts\` (cn() helper):** Merge Tailwind classes with \`tailwind-merge\` to avoid conflicting utilities.
- **Pattern \`components/ui/button.tsx\` (Button variants):** Use \`class-variance-authority\` (cva) for size and variant props on shadcn \`Button\`.
- **Pattern \`app/layout.tsx\` (App layout shell):** Root layout wraps providers (\`ThemeProvider\`, \`Toaster\`) and font loading.
- **Avoid:** Do not hand-edit \`components.json\` or generated shadcn files without running the CLI.
- **Avoid:** Avoid fetching in Client Components when the same data can be loaded in a Server Component.
- **Avoid:** Do not add new CSS files per page; extend Tailwind tokens or use \`cn()\` instead.
- **Common task (Add a shadcn UI primitive):** 1. Run \`pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component>\` from the repo root. 2. Import from \`@/components/ui/<component>\` in your feature code. 3. Use \`cn()\` from \`@/lib/utils\` when merging classes. 4. Run \`pnpm lint\` and \`pnpm test\` before opening a PR."
`;
